inputs.prompt:
A fearless woman launches into a skateboard trick mid-air, frozen at the peak of motion. Her body is perfectly balanced and athletic, knees bent, arms extended for control as the board flips beneath her feet. She wears bold, expressive street fashion—oversized jacket flowing behind her, textured fabric catching the wind, layered accessories adding motion and attitude. Her expression is focused and determined, eyes locked on the landing.

The scene takes place in an urban environment at golden hour, warm sunlight streaking across concrete and steel. Motion blur trails from the skateboard wheels, dust and particles suspended in the air. The camera angle is low and close, emphasizing height, speed, and power. Crisp detail on the subject, dynamic lighting, shallow depth of field, cinematic action photography style, high energy, modern youth culture aesthetic.
